01:22:54,053 --> 01:22:56,971
You have slain my love.

1205
01:22:57,056 --> 01:23:00,642
Well, he is dead,
and where shall I find another?

1206
01:23:00,726 --> 01:23:04,687
It takes years to train
a man to love me.

1207
01:23:05,272 --> 01:23:10,360
Where shall I find another?

1208
01:23:14,365 --> 01:23:15,865
Here.

1209
01:23:16,450 --> 01:23:18,034
Here!

1210
01:23:18,118 --> 01:23:20,119
What?

1211
01:23:20,204 --> 01:23:25,083
Katisha, for years I have loved
you with a white-hot passion...

1212
01:23:25,167 --> 01:23:29,671
which is slowly but surely
consuming my very vitals!

1213
01:23:34,093 --> 01:23:37,887
Ah, shrink not from me.

1214
01:23:42,476 --> 01:23:44,143
Kat -

1215
01:23:45,646 --> 01:23:49,524
Katisha, I dare not
hope for your love...

1216
01:23:49,608 --> 01:23:51,734
but I will not live without it.

1217
01:23:51,819 --> 01:23:53,528
Darling!

1218
01:23:53,612 --> 01:23:57,490
You! You, whose hands still reek
with the blood of my betrothed...

1219
01:23:57,574 --> 01:24:01,869
dare to address words of passion to
the woman you have so foully wronged?

1220
01:24:01,954 --> 01:24:06,958
I do. Accept my love,
or I perish on the spot!

1221
01:24:13,006 --> 01:24:14,924
Go to!

1222
01:24:15,008 --> 01:24:19,971
Who knows so well as I that no one
ever yet died of a broken heart.

1223
01:24:21,890 --> 01:24:24,767
You know not what you say.

1224
01:24:28,856 --> 01:24:31,065
Listen.

1225
