♪ On a tree by a river a little tomtit ♪

1226
01:24:36,363 --> 01:24:39,991
♪ Sang
Willow, tit-willow, tit-willow ♪

1227
01:24:40,075 --> 01:24:43,786
♪ And I said to him
Dickey bird, why do you sit ♪

1228
01:24:43,871 --> 01:24:47,665
♪ Singing
Willow, tit-willow, tit-willow ♪

1229
01:24:47,750 --> 01:24:52,795
