1260
01:27:17,941 --> 01:27:20,526
Have all the painful
preparations been made?

1261
01:27:20,611 --> 01:27:22,528
Your Majesty, all is prepared.

1262
01:27:22,613 --> 01:27:24,780
Then produce the
unfortunate gentleman...

1263
01:27:24,865 --> 01:27:28,784
and his two well-meaning
but misguided accomplices.

1264
01:27:50,724 --> 01:27:53,893
Mercy for Ko-Ko.
Mercy for Pitti-Sing.

1265
01:27:53,977 --> 01:27:56,020
Mercy even for Pooh-Bah.

1266
01:27:56,104 --> 01:27:58,648
