Mercy even for Pooh-Bah.

1268
01:28:02,903 --> 01:28:04,987
My husband that was
to have been is dead...

1269
01:28:05,072 --> 01:28:08,616
and I have just married
this, uh, miserable object.

1270
01:28:11,703 --> 01:28:14,914
Oh. You've not been long about it.

1271
01:28:15,540 --> 01:28:18,334
No. We were married
before the registrar.

1272
01:28:18,418 --> 01:28:20,586
I am the registrar.

1273
01:28:20,671 --> 01:28:21,837
I see.

1274
01:28:21,922 --> 01:28:26,092
But my difficulty is that, as
you have slain the heir apparent -

1275
01:28:39,690 --> 01:28:43,567
