practically, it is done -

1285
01:29:12,222 --> 01:29:14,557
because Your Majesty's will is law.

1286
01:29:14,641 --> 01:29:16,809
Your Majesty says,
"Kill a gentleman" -

1287
01:29:16,893 --> 01:29:19,562
Well, a gentleman is
told off to be killed.

1288
01:29:19,646 --> 01:29:22,064
Consequently,
that gentleman is as good as dead -

1289
01:29:22,149 --> 01:29:24,692
practically, he is dead.

1290
01:29:25,360 --> 01:29:28,738
Well, if he is dead,
why not say so?

1291
